sequenceDiagram
    participant User as User
    participant App as Mobile/Web App
    participant Server as Backend Server
    participant ML as ML Models
    participant Ext as External Services

    User->>+App: Capture/Upload Image
    App->>+Server: Send Image (HTTPS, AES-256)
    Server->>+ML: Analyze Image (Face, Object, Depth, Landmarks)
    ML-->>-Server: Biometric Features
    Server->>Server: Temporary Storage & Immediate Deletion
    Server-->>-App: Analysis Results
    App-->>-User: Display Results & Feedback
    Server->>+Ext: Sync/Authenticate/Control (Health, Identity, IoT)
    Ext-->>-Server: Acknowledge/Response
